Title: An Act Changing the Name of Barangay Lower Ipil Heights in the Municipality of Ipil, Province of Zamboanga Del Sur, to Barangay Tirso Babiera
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA BLG. 658
An Act Changing the Name of Barangay Lower Ipil Heights in the Municipality of Ipil, Province of Zamboanga Del Sur, to Barangay Tirso Babiera
Section 1. The name of Barangay Lower Ipil Heights the Municipality of Ipil, Province of Zamboanga del Sur, is hereby changed to Barangay Tirso Babiera.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: March 7, 1984
